  body
    .app-container.container-fluid
      .app-row.row
        .app-sidebar.col-md-3
          .panel.panel-default
            .panel-heading Site Name
            .panel-body
              p This first paragraph should have text explaining the site, what it can be used for and why itâ€™s important.
